{"tid":316570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［野外騎乘］台短裙少女捷運站外騎在男友上博命搖","createTime":"2017-07-10T23:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T00:33:40.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43c57511db8c8906ed423cc83ef171a9517ac2ee","tid":316570,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T23:15:53.000Z","msg":"有網友在臉書專頁《爆料公社》分享一段年輕情侶疑在捷運站附近「活春宮」影片引發熱烈討論，影片全長僅25秒，一對看起來還只是學生的男女坐在捷運站附近的石椅上，女生穿著短裙跨坐在男生下半部，男生則扶著女生的腰不斷的搖，看起來就像是在從事某項「活塞運動」，如此公開透明令人看了臉紅心跳。<br />\n許多網友都覺得太誇張，有網友表示「好誇張」「嗯...年輕真好」「至少找個草叢吧」「現在的小孩真的好誇張」「連上賓館的錢都省了」「搖搖馬嗎？」，但也有網友認為「感覺假的」「不就女孩坐在男孩大腿上而已」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170710/1157830/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170710%2F1157830%2F&d=L6CV2RtxdhgWp4WDfg6CNQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=70c8bdd2\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170710/1157830/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/071519_38778fcd21d13ea6703eb0806d2eeaa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F071519_38778fcd21d13ea6703eb0806d2eeaa3.jpg&h=fbcdbc27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係土地問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c02542e13cb71995397b2ed43c53a2c068f973b","tid":316570,"uid":14331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T23:24:42.000Z","msg":"鏡頭搖多過條女搖"},{"pid":"584d52a8ddc3cfb2e4b927b89684e47ae6ee52b8","tid":316570,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T00:33:40.000Z","msg":"連登又做孤兒仔"}]}